      <title>巴尔金：美联储有能力应对经济形势变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-12/fed-in-good-place-to-respond-however-economy-evolves-barkin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里士满联邦储备银行行长托马斯·巴尔金表示，美国经济形势良好，这使得美国央行“无论经济如何发展，都能做出适当反应”。巴尔金周二在巴尔的摩峰会上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-12/fed-in-good-place-to-respond-however-economy-evolves-barkin</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 16:42:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
